ck with my current fix. The three sed commands should handle removing `deprecated` from the features list in most cases.\n\n[HYBRID]: Strategy guided by expert knowledge about hyper version incompatibility, but implementation details derived from analyzing the specific Cargo.toml format and sed pattern requirements.'}
